edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.tasks

Class RouteResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.tasks.RouteResult

  • public class RouteResult
extends com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
    The result from the Route Task. The RouteResult properties are dependent on the RouteParameter inputs. For example, directions are only returned if RouteParameters.returnDirections is set to "true".
    Author:
    Justin Merz
